持黑警既藝人係咪大撚曬先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75802fa2e5d37b4aa973f136f46534f73f88226","tid":2144854,"uid":42250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T18:59:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4510780962065818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4510780962065818&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6EngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=04f31c1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/status/4510780962065818</a><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">之前疏通曬</span></span>, 最後武士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊明莊思明<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">外賣贈警隊</span></span> 楊明:代表所有良好市民向警員致謝<br />\n<br />\n黑暴禍港將近一年，全靠警察流血流汗守護香港。今日楊明與女友莊思明<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">帶同大量外賣送予警員</span></span>，楊明更代表所有良好市民向警察致謝。據悉，這些外賣均由一位剛過身的老婆婆捐出，她生前的心願就是希望將所有積蓄購買食物送予每位警員，老婆婆的心願最終由契女拜托楊明完成。楊明莊思明最後表示，希望全體警員加油，大家保重身體，平平安安。"},{"pid":"a67ef2712f2475905acbd75a598e38b5deefe165","tid":2144854,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T18:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ad7rRHz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fad7rRHz.png&h=d47f2cda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4NSNfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4NSNfV.jpg&h=9d32ae3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收禮指引都改埋<br />\n零食當係警察福利冇上限<br />\n你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd911fbbfa3abeb32ee7b836f017a7f92f368e8c","tid":2144854,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T19:01:19.000Z","msg":"要兩個散仔食死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cbbc1a2f9464fe3d5b65c830676d4ec04bd1da","tid":2144854,"uid":108631,"like":0,"dislike":0,